text: Ishmuratovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Staroisayevsky Selsoviet, Nurimanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 223 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 30 km from Krasnaya Gorka, 15 km from Starokulevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Nurimanovsky District
title: Ishmuratovo
